title: India Plans Taiwan Labor Supply Pact While China Tensions Brew
selftext:
After Israel wanting to bring in 100k workers from India now Taiwan also wants to do the same: 

India-Taiwan employment agreement to be inked as early as Dec.

As many as 100,000 Indians can apply for jobs in Taiwan.
